metadata.name: HAI Summer
metadata.description: At the heart of “HAI” is the AI Manga, that blends manga & other art styles through the use of AI. "HAI" not only reflects the Japanese word for "yes" or "I understand," but also references "AI" within the title. In the realm of artificial intelligence, 'HAI Summer' captures the essence of the chaotic summer ahead, where unexpected adventures & overwhelming human emotions collide, reminding us to embrace the unpredictable with open eyes.
